window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The mad king will kill us all.</b><br> <b>He’s trying to tear the universe apart, and I’m the last obstacle in his path.</b></p> <p>We beat the City’s strongest battle mages, but the invasion was only a distraction. While we fought his lackeys, King Emil had his eye on a bigger prize: the Fae Realm. </p> <p>He wants immortality, and he’s going to destroy the universe to get it. We’re out of time and the stakes are impossibly high. If I want my new babies to live in a world of dragons, I have to face the cruel king on his own playing field. </p> <p>If my mates and I don’t stop him, the rifts King Emil is creating will destroy everything. It’s time to stare down the void. </p> <p><b><i>Bliss Evermore</i></b><b> is the fifth and final book in The Fae Dragon’s Harem, a paranormal reverse harem FMMMMM series containing MM scenes. The new series, The Fae Thief’s Harem, begins on June 1, 2021. Scroll up, and preorder now, and dive into a whole new world of magic, danger, and passion…and dragons who won’t let anything get between them and their final fated mate.</b></p>"; 
